text: Executive Support Officer Do you have experience delivering executive support services, have an eye for detail and want to contribute to our diverse organisation? We are seeking a skilled administrator who will provide executive assistance and support to our Executive Assistant, Deputy CEO, and across our Business Growth & Community directorate. Applications close midnight 10 October 2021. Please note: Applications may close earlier for the right candidate.
